Package: wright.pkg
Title: An R package for processing shrubbery data
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: c(
  person(given = "April",
          family = "Wright",
          role = c("cre", "aut"),
          email = "april.wright@selu.edu")
          )
Description: An R package to process plant data. Most functions accept numerical input and allow users to calculate a variety of summary statistics to understand plants in their ecosystems. Users can use this to calculate popular and widely-used stats such as whatever, this and that, and some other stuff.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
